org.ow2.proactive.scheduler.job

Class ClientJobState

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.ow2.proactive.scheduler.common.task.CommonAttribute
      • org.ow2.proactive.scheduler.common.job.Job
        • org.ow2.proactive.scheduler.common.job.JobState
          • org.ow2.proactive.scheduler.job.ClientJobState
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<JobState>

    public class ClientJobState
extends JobState
    This class is a client view of a JobState. A client will receive an instance of this class when connecting to the scheduler front-end and ask for a JobState (for instance by using Scheduler.getJobState(String)). The value of some attributes will not be available in this view of the JobState. Therefore, calling the respective getters will throw a RuntimeException. See the public method's javadoc for more details.
